    "In particular, the limitρ X C:= lim n↑∞ ρ X Cn,exists and defines a unital *-endomorphism of A.",
    "Moreover, ρ X C is supported on supp (C) in the sense that if x ∈ A supp (C) c then ρ X C (x) = x.",
